In chess, the world number one Magnus Carlsen achieves the highest-ever FIDE official rating (2861) based on Elo rating system, breaking Garry Kasparov's 13-year record. (FIDE) (ChessBase) (ABC.es)2014 FIFA World Cup host Brazil will play Italy in a friendly game in Geneva, Switzerland, on 21 March 2013 ahead of their 2013 FIFA Confederations Cup match on 22 June 2013 in Salvador, Bahia. (Goal.com) (ESPN)